INSERT INTO `comments` VALUES (1,142,'<br><br>From the get-go, Helen (the office manager) was sincerely warm and courteous. The ease of making an appointment was a BREEZE!! FYI.. they schedule and ensure that each patient gets quality service from the doctors! No overbooking like in medical offices where one has to wait forever to be seen!!! Location was easy to find, since I work out at Synergy (gym next door). Once I entered the office, it was very ZEN! Calming, very spiritual and relaxing!! Dr. Stanley had outstanding bedside manner and answered ALL of my questions and concerns!! I had gone through 3 Acupuncturists in the past, but my experience with this place was AMAZING!! Dr. Stanley knew where all my trouble spots were just by looking at my ear! How cool is that ?!? Overall I was extremely pleased with my visit and plan on going back! Best of all, they are open 7 days / week and accept Insurance!!<br><br>Amy T. (Albany, NY)<br>','Amy T.','',1,'June 15, 2015  6:06 PM','226d50048d44184b0664654f1c398395ed27488858b20aa643893373feca0e9088115538ec272628','1434405960','939858161'),(6,142,'<br>Hurt my back the other day and was literally on my hands and knees. Went to my PCP and he gave me a prescription for pain killers, which did nothing! A buddy of mine highly recommended BMT Acupuncture. Never had it done before, just the thought of being a pin cushion gives me the chills! Was in excruciating pain, and nothing else worked, so I gave them a shot. (No pun intended). The doctors there were compassionate, understanding and highly experienced!! Literally within minutes, my pain was gone!! I am a believer and highly recommend this place to everyone I come across!<br>-Steve T. (Hempstead, NY)','Steve T.','',1,'July 9, 2015  11:09 AM','18a7ecc6d1ab7b1084c89388054f822d0b72aff621983fccd46691bae06ad5285fbac40df2a3b200','1436454540','1405121426'),(7,142,'I never tried acupuncture before but after 2 foot surgeries and being told by at least 6 doctors that I will have to live with the pain in my foot I decided to try it. WOW. For the first time in 8 years, I was able to wear a shoe with a heel at a formal event and I walk every day pain free. Stanley is amazing and can asses my acupuncture needs perfectly. I hate needles but Stanley is so gentle that I have no problems with the treatment and it&rsquo;s such a relaxing environment that I look forward to each session. I even fall asleep on the table! I highly recommend BMT and they even accept my insurance!<br>Ellen D. (Oceanside, NY)','Ellen D.','',1,'July 16, 2015  9:04 AM','35b72845d9f06de49a439669f574dcdb0b5111139b644f34739a64fb2705994fcccee3553eaab5cd','1437051840','1279601265'),(8,142,'I have been going to Stanley for approximately one year now, and he is amazing!<br>Stanley is very thorough, caring, accommodating, and knowledgeable of both eastern and western medicine. He is very realistic about what he can or cannot treat, and truly cares if you are experiencing results. For example, I went in when I had a sinus infection; later that day I was almost completely cleared and could breath.<br>I would definitely recommend Stanley to anyone who has not tried acupuncture before, or someone who is looking to try someone new. The best part is that he accepts insurance, which greatly reduces the cost of acupuncture. I don&rsquo;t have to pay anything when I see him, how can you beat that. My friend who also sees Stanley does not have insurance that covers acupuncture, but they were able to work something out to make the cost of treatment affordable.<br>Overall, I highly recommend Stanley, and think everyone should try acupuncture at least once!<br>Mark L Lynbrook, NY','Mark L','email in old db if you need',1,'August 1, 2015  8:25 PM','c7f5530b7919925a4da1397ef6264f4f985bd90a3a85677f66ae4d0c68b77c5d7168c3b397f00fc8','1438475100','949736009'),(9,142,'AMAZING!! What a soothing and relaxing atmosphere! I could not move my neck when I arrived. By the time my session was over, not only could I move my neck, I was completely relaxed. Dr. Stanley is, by far, the best Acupuncturist I ever went to!!<br>Ginny F. (Rockville Centre, NY)','Ginny F.','email in old db if you need',1,'August 4, 2015  1:12 PM','b7b3a349e571cf2fb4e93c1523e7a9ad6ad97777b868cfb220159039fe10c894f96209c03464efec','1438708320','2068710264'),(10,142,'All I can say is, once again the pain is gone. I used to go to him at his old place after I had back surgery because my strength wasn&rsquo;t returning to my left arm due to nerve damage and I waited for 3 years, while lifting weights with no progress. After just 4 sessions with Stanley, my bench press was right back to where it should be.<br>My session today involved pain in my neck and arm, a pain I&rsquo;m familiar with. Between the acupuncture and the deep tissue massage by one of his massage therapists, the pain is gone.<br>Matt B. (Glenn Cove, NY)','Matt B.','email in old db if you need',1,'August 7, 2015   3:16 PM','d3710911253f19950a6642cbc90af0d446e5dd9d4b02eb072db28d61b7046202e2d4079f75369fa7','1438974960','115956558'),(11,142,'<br>I had every test possible for my leg pains and many doctors offered no help. A friend of mine suggested acupuncture after seeing an ad by Stanley. I felt he was a miracle worker. His technique and manner were so soothing I looked forward to my visits to see him.','Valerie H','blueoceanmama@gmail.com',1,'August 8, 2015  3:10 PM','1b27c7455d35c79e3a559ac6717eb4c8b5e29d89bf7dec7a6db4cfe4eb61a63a11c78ae3cfb5fcd9','1439061000','1944699689'),(12,142,'Great Atmosphere, Dr. Yuan &amp; Staff are Amazing =)','Monique S.','',1,'October 8, 2015  4:02 PM','bbfebcd7ed3d10237ff6d3b9de22057264f7cedbb6fbe6f03767cb4ca453378d4ba91f45394a2426','1444334520','2015459342'),(13,142,'I would like to highlight one of our local businesses. Stanley Yuan LAc owner of BMT Acupuncture is wonderful! He is extremely compassionate and amazing with children. If you are looking for an acupuncturist definitely give him a call. He grew up in Oceanside and is now raising his family here. Great person!','Julie A.','email in old db if you need',1,'March 23, 2016  10:21 PM','8817f4e8e9cdc6edc162e953b0d4d725fa95ee357ee95363490c61882a386d502a21c46254bed697','1458786060','12143811'),(14,142,'I haven&rsquo;t gotten acupuncture and cupping therapy treatment in three years and I decided to go in for cupping therapy last night since I have been feeling the weight of the world on my shoulders. I went into see my friend, Stanley Yuan LAc for cupping therapy. He was thorough and caring through the whole process. After cupping and a massage, I felt a lot of the tension released. If you have not tried either treatment, feel free to call him to discuss which treatment might work for you. He is knowledgeable in both Eastern and Western medicine. Best part is he takes insurance. If you don&rsquo;t have it, he will work a suitable payment.','Gilat N.','email in old db if you need',1,'August 13, 2016  9:27 AM','d83fe58f72eb93ec1f794d5dd7b410636e40b42b68c885210eaec5b757c9546b9f58d7bf5c1de11c','1471094820','117518515'),(15,142,'I went to see Stanley today, whom was very nice. I have lot of issues, but couldn&rsquo;t afford the sessions due to my current financial situation. He was very accommodating and as a result, had suggested to get bodywork done which felt great! I will definitely be back once I have more money saved up.','Mary H.','email in old db if you need',1,'August 15, 2016  3:02 PM','4bf96054e4457c8df20a8689438181822793d88d731a3482190917fe19c50808b3170377abca8fab','1471287720','1029718004'),(16,142,'Have gone to BMT Acupuncture several times throughout the year already for various issues. Facility is wonderful and staff were great! Will certainly be returning again soon.','Casey S.','email in old db if you need',1,'October 3, 2016  2:13 PM','e04ad5e01928937203fd09742d805c35817684aee7d730868b5a29025fd9a96284e0d4700338adb7','1475518380','689301834'),(17,142,'I have been suffering from Low back and sciatic pain for the past 2 weeks. Afraid of pain and have a HUGE phobia of needles, but have tried everything else with no success. Stanley was referred to me by a very close friend whom said to have helped her immensely, so I decided to give him a try. Upon entering the office, the atmosphere was very serene and tranquil. I found Stanley and his staff very knowledgeable and experienced. He explained everything in detail to me which put me at ease. He placed something on my ear and on my nose, and the pain decreased within minutes! Felt totally relaxed and maybe even dozed off during the session. After getting off the table, pain was definitely much better. The next morning, woke up PAIN FREE!!! Will definitely be back again this week for follow up and maintenance!','Deb B.','email in old db if you need',1,'October 17, 2016  3:00 PM','41fb8d4906ab7b4b677eb08b55a9be6b1d45e8b5c2957a1d6a1ec3868a0860b7710b03fc8c0bbf04','1476730800','1670616293'),(18,142,'Wanted to highly recommend Stanley Yuan LAc BMT Acupuncture! (Oceanside dad)<br>I went to him to try acupuncture and it was extremely relaxing and he made the experience very comfortable. Highly recommend him!!<br>Courtney K. (Oceanside, NY)','Courtney K.','email in old db if you need',1,'November 15, 2016  12:11 PM','111535a72433251073956cf18bfe2853bb64b0b9f461fdb5711a1703d42ab92ffc7359eb71adfcec','1479229860','871192423'),(19,142,'Just want to say thank you to Stanley Yuan LAc from BMT acupuncture in Baldwin Harbor. You are a true healer. I have been bed ridden for the past few days with a herniated disk and the acupuncture, seeds &amp; cupping treatment you have given me has honestly helped me more than what the orthopedist did for me. Thanks again! <br>Evelyn T. (Oceanside, NY)','Evelyn T.','',1,'November 15, 2016  12:12 PM','4ef361a2857fbf6d277fe55b5d89366fb0935ece5f7e4a1b28c3bd97bf1da2ec51b37594e02efbee','1479229920','1156345196'),(20,142,'Just wanna give a HUGE shoutout to Dr Stanley Yuan and BMT Acupuncture ! By far one of the best 